         <div type="abstract">
            <p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_1908"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__beatrix_von_zollern_nuernberg_QGW_II_I_1048"><roleName type="title">Herzogin</roleName> Beatrix<roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-burgkapelle-messe_beatrix_von_zollern_nuernberg"><add>zu Lehen geht</add></roleName></rs></rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">genehmigt<add> verkauft</add><add> gekauft
                     habe</add></triggerstring>, dass <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="pe__petrus_von_mautern_QGW_II_II_1908">Peter von Mauttarn, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-burgkapelle-messe_beatrix_von_zollern_nuernberg">kaplan</roleName> Unsrer Fraun mess in der Purkch ze Wienn, die von ihr
                        zu Lehen geht</rs>,</rs>
                  <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_1908_men_1"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__petrus_von_mautern_QGW_II_II_1908"><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-burgkapelle-messe_beatrix_von_zollern_nuernberg"><add>kaplan</add></roleName></rs></rs><rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_kohlmarkt_31">ein Haus <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-kohlmarkt">an
                              dem</roleName>
                           <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-kohlmarkt">Kolmarkcht</rs>
                           <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-st_michael">gegen <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-st_michael">sant Michel</rs>
                              über</roleName>, <roleName type="owner" corresp="pe__johann_QGW_II_II_1908">das weilent <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_QGW_II_II_1908">Hannsen, des <roleName type="prof">harnaschmaister</roleName>
                                 <roleName type="dead">seligen</roleName></rs>, gewesen
                              ist</roleName></rs></rs> , <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II">um
                           <measure>129 lb dn.</measure></rs>
                     <triggerstring n="disp">verkauft</triggerstring></rs> und <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_1908_men_2"><rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II">dafür<measure>
                           <add>129 lb dn.</add></measure></rs>
                     <rs type="fn" role="recipient">zu <rs type="person" ref="pe__petrus_von_mautern_QGW_II_II_1908"><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-burgkapelle-messe_beatrix_von_zollern_nuernberg"><add>kaplan</add></roleName></rs><rs type="org" ref="org__wien-burgkapelle-messe_beatrix_von_zollern_nuernberg">der
                           Messe</rs></rs>
                     <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_st_agnes_auf_der_himmelpforte_11">ein anderes Haus
                              <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-st_agnes_auf_der_himmelpforte">bei der</roleName>
                           <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-st_agnes_auf_der_himmelpforte">Himelporten</rs>
                           <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-immo_st_poeltner_hof">gegen <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_st_poeltner_hof">Pöltinger
                                 hoff</rs> über</roleName>, <roleName type="owner" corresp="pe__bonacurs_QGW_II_II_1908">das weilent <rs type="person" ref="pe__bonacurs_QGW_II_II_1908"><roleName type="title">maister</roleName> Bonacurs</rs> gewesen
                        ist</roleName></rs>,</rs>
                     <triggerstring n="disp">gekauft habe</triggerstring></rs>.</rs>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="nota">
            <p>Indorsate: a) ain Urlaubbrief von von Nuremberg uber, b) fraun Beatriczen ain haus,
